  "item.description.unshattered.gabagool_the_fish": "If the salad is on top, I send it back.",
  "item.description.unshattered.gift_the_fish": "I'm empty inside.",
  "item.description.unshattered.herring_the_fish": "Sometimes patience is the key to victory. Sometimes it leads to very little and it seems like it's not worth it. And you wonder why you waited so long for something so disappointing.",
  "item.description.unshattered.nope_the_fish": "Why did we follow Shrimp...",
  "item.description.unshattered.oops_the_fish": "Discovered in the depths of the island during the summer months.",
  "item.description.unshattered.party_the_fish": "Big fan of parties, yet it's hard to enjoy them without friends.",
  "item.description.unshattered.rock_the_fish": "Don't take me for granite.",
  "item.description.unshattered.shrimp_the_fish": "I achieved nothing.",
  "item.description.unshattered.skeleton_the_fish": "Once a beautiful bass, but his loud mouth got the better of him.",
  "item.description.unshattered.spook_the_fish": "This fish lurks in the darkness below the island during the Halloween season.",
  "item.description.unshattered.stew_the_fish": "The stew was expired.",
  "item.description.unshattered.swamp_the_fish": "I once tried a clear pond. too shiny. Never again.",
  "item.description.unshattered.zoop_the_fish": "Keep me in here please.",
  "item.description.unshattered.fig_log": "Each ring tells tales of sun-kissed days. Hold it close, and you might hear its stories.",
